{"tid":1125990,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有沒有人知道e隻咩黎","createTime":"2019-04-26T05:27:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T12:14:46.000Z","uid":213533,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"79b2906440a3e7411e607b4e0710b5dc8126295e","tid":1125990,"uid":213533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T05:27:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RvrD33A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRvrD33A.jpg&h=56656ae8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好大隻，識飛好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用掃把打左好多下都唔死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n包括大家見到張圖<br />\n<br />\n我一掃佢去垃圾鏟時即刻返身爬<br />\n我好彩快快手扔左隻野落膠袋<br />\n跟手扔左出去<br />\n（隻野係袋入面仲爬緊）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n應該不是小強<br />\n未見過咁大隻小強<br />\n兩條觸比小強長好多<br />\n個強有d白色點<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嚇死我了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b14f55f36d24e473b1a186a373263621a02495b6","tid":1125990,"uid":213196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T05:27:57.000Z","msg":"RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"254f02fc92cc8c10137d00570155955f4b9b1e4c","tid":1125990,"uid":1637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T05:30:56.000Z","msg":"天牛"},{"pid":"7abc114cba21d8a1aec643c67acd1bbcc44395a4","tid":1125990,"uid":213533,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"254f02fc92cc8c10137d00570155955f4b9b1e4c","tid":1125990,"uid":1637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T05:30:5